<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.2.2">
<l>nīṇilā muṟṟattu niṉṟivaḷ nōkkiṉāḷ,</l>
<l>kāṇumō kaṇṇa purameṉṟu kāṭṭiṉāḷ</l>
<l>pāṇaṉār tiṇṇa mirukka viṉiyivaḷ</l>
<l>nāṇumō naṉṟunaṉ ṟunaṟai yūrarkkē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Standing in the courtyard with the moonlight on high, she gazed;</l>
<l>Saying, “Do we see Kaṇṇapuram?” she pointed.</l>
<l>Since the bards’ abilities are [such], will she still be modest?</l>
<l>The benefit is excellent for him of Naṟaiyūr!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
